<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>Golf Instruction — Christophe Stutts</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{background:#F4F1EA;font-family:"Inter",sans-serif;color:#1a1a1a;min-height:100vh}
.hero{background:#0D1F0F;padding:52px 48px 44px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hero-geo{position:absolute;right:0;top:0;width:220px;height:220px;border-left:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);border-bottom-left-radius:220px}
.hero-geo2{position:absolute;right:30px;top:30px;width:160px;height:160px;border-left:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.08);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.08);border-bottom-left-radius:160px}
.hero-inner{max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;position:relative}
.hero-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C9A84C;margin-bottom:12px}
.hero-name{font-family:"Bebas Neue",sans-serif;font-size:72px;line-height:.9;color:#F5F0E8;letter-spacing:.04em}
.hero-sub{font-size:14px;font-weight:300;color:rgba(245,240,232,0.55);margin-top:14px;letter-spacing:.04em}
.hero-contact{display:flex;gap:24px;margin-top:20px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.hero-contact span{font-size:12px;color:rgba(245,240,232,0.6)}
.hero-contact span b{color:#C9A84C;font-weight:400}
.creds-strip{display:flex;gap:10px;margin-top:28px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center}
.cred-pill{background:#fff;border-radius:6px;padding:5px 10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;height:40px}
.cred-pill img{height:28px;width:auto;max-width:90px;object-fit:contain;display:block}
.page{max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;padding:48px 24px 72px}
.section-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1B4D2E;margin-bottom:20px}
.packages{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:48px}
.pkg{background:#fff;border-radius:10px;padding:28px;border:1px solid #e2ded6;position:relative}
.pkg.featured{border:2px solid #1B4D2E}
.pkg-badge{position:absolute;top:-10px;left:20px;background:#1B4D2E;color:#fff;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px}
.pkg-name{font-family:"Bebas Neue",sans-serif;font-size:24px;letter-spacing:.04em;color:#0D1F0F;margin-bottom:2px}
.pkg-duration{font-size:11px;color:#888;margin-bottom:18px}
.pkg-price{font-family:"Bebas Neue",sans-serif;font-size:56px;line-height:1;color:#1B4D2E}
.pkg-price span{font-family:"Inter",sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:400;color:#888;margin-left:3px}
.pkg-divider{height:1px;background:#f0ece4;margin:18px 0}
.pkg-features{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:9px}
.pkg-features li{font-size:12.5px;color:#555;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;line-height:1.4}
.pkg-features li::before{content:"";width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:#C9A84C;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:5px}
.bottom-cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:48px}
.bcard{background:#fff;border-radius:10px;padding:24px;border:1px solid #e2ded6}
.bcard-tag{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C9A84C;margin-bottom:8px}
.bcard-title{font-family:"Bebas Neue",sans-serif;font-size:20px;color:#0D1F0F;letter-spacing:.03em;margin-bottom:10px}
.bcard-body{font-size:12.5px;color:#666;line-height:1.7}
.note{background:#fff;border-radius:10px;padding:22px 24px;border:1px solid #e2ded6;font-size:12.5px;color:#666;line-height:1.7}
.note b{color:#0D1F0F;font-weight:600}
.footer{background:#0D1F0F;padding:28px 48px;text-align:center}
.footer p{font-size:11.5px;color:rgba(245,240,232,0.4);letter-spacing:.04em}
.footer b{color:#C9A84C;font-weight:400}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-geo"></div>
  <div class="hero-geo2"></div>
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-label">Golf Instruction</div>
    <div class="hero-name">Christophe<br>Stutts</div>
    <div class="hero-sub">Wekiva Golf Club &middot; Longwood, FL &middot; Private Instruction</div>
    <div class="hero-contact">
      <span><b>(407) 404-2211</b></span>
      <span><b>cstutts6golf@gmail.com</b></span>
    </div>
    <div class="creds-strip">
      <div class="cred-pill"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="University of Florida"></div>
      <div class="cred-pill"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="PGA Tour Americas"></div>
      <div class="cred-pill"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="PGA Tour Latinoamerica"></div>
      <div class="cred-pill"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Gira Profesional Mexicana"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="page">

  <div class="section-label">Rates</div>
  <div class="packages">
    <div class="pkg">
      <div class="pkg-name">Range Lesson</div>
      <div class="pkg-duration">1 hour &middot; Driving range</div>
      <div class="pkg-price">$80<span>/ session</span></div>
      <div class="pkg-divider"></div>
      <ul class="pkg-features">
        <li>Full swing, short game, or putting focus</li>
        <li>Video analysis available</li>
        <li>Drill plan + written recap after every session</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="pkg featured">
      <div class="pkg-badge">Recommended</div>
      <div class="pkg-name">Playing Lesson</div>
      <div class="pkg-duration">9 holes on course &middot; ~2 hours</div>
      <div class="pkg-price">$130<span>/ round</span></div>
      <div class="pkg-divider"></div>
      <ul class="pkg-features">
        <li>Course management &amp; real-game decisions</li>
        <li>Pre-shot routine &amp; mental approach</li>
        <li>Shot-by-shot feedback throughout the round</li>
        <li>Written recap with key takeaways</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-label">Additional services</div>
  <div class="bottom-cards">
    <div class="bcard">
      <div class="bcard-tag">Flexible</div>
      <div class="bcard-title">Lesson Packages</div>
      <div class="bcard-body">If you're committed to improving and want to book multiple sessions, reach out directly. I'm happy to work out a rate that reflects that commitment. Packages are tailored — just get in touch.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bcard">
      <div class="bcard-tag">Junior players</div>
      <div class="bcard-title">College Recruiting Consultation</div>
      <div class="bcard-body">Navigating the D1 recruiting process from the inside — school targeting, coach outreach, tournament exposure, and building a profile that gets noticed. Every player's situation is different, so pricing is discussed after an initial conversation.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="note">
    <b>How it works:</b> Every session includes a written recap — what we worked on, drills to practice, and the one thing to take away. Lessons are held at Wekiva Golf Club. To book or ask about packages, reach out directly by phone or email.
  </div>

</div>

<div class="footer">
  <p>Christophe Stutts &middot; Golf Instruction &middot; Wekiva Golf Club &middot; <b>(407) 404-2211</b> &middot; cstutts6golf@gmail.com</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
